          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 animate-in-up animate-delay-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/angad-singh97" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-pop inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/40 hover:border-accent-cyan hover:text-accent-cyan hover:bg-accent-cyan/5 min-h-touch sm:min-h-0" aria-label="GitHub">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
              GitHub
            </a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/angad-sde-nyc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-pop inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/40 hover:border-accent-cyan hover:text-accent-cyan hover:bg-accent-cyan/5 min-h-touch sm:min-h-0" aria-label="LinkedIn">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
