          <span class="text-accent-lime">ðŸš€</span> Featured Research & Projects
        </h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- SBUnix -->
          <article class="hover-lift group rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 sm:p-5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-accent-amber/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-8px_rgba(251,191,36,0.2)] transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-display font-bold text-accent-amber mb-2">
              <a href="https://compas.cs.stonybrook.edu/cse506-v3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">
                SBUnix â€” Coming Soon
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-accent-amber/90 mb-2 font-medium">Full Unix-like OS from scratch</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light mb-2 leading-snug">Kernel, file system (TARFS), virtual memory, preemptive scheduling, COW fork(), user-mode processes (ring 3). Shell (SBUsh), init, syscalls (fork, execve, pipe), libc (sblibc). C + assembly.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-cpp-blue/20 text-cpp-blue border border-cpp-blue/40">C</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-amber/20 text-tag-amber border border-tag-amber/40">Assembly</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- User-Space Networking -->
          <article class="hover-lift group rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 sm:p-5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-cpp-blue/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-8px_rgba(86,156,214,0.25)] transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-display font-bold text-cpp-blue mb-2">
              <a href="https://github.com/angad-singh97/riscv-network-stack" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">
                User-Space Networking on RISC-V
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-cpp-blue/90 mb-2 font-medium">DPDK + F-Stack on RISC-V FPGA</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light mb-2 leading-snug">Custom PMD for a proprietary NIC. Solved hardware race from RISC-V weak memory model with assembly <code class="text-terminal-green px-1 rounded bg-charcoal">FENCE</code>s. Zero-copy DMA via Hugepages and vfio-platform.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-cpp-blue/20 text-cpp-blue border border-cpp-blue/40">C</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-terminal-green/20 text-terminal-green border border-terminal-green/40">RISC-V</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-amber/20 text-tag-amber border border-tag-amber/40">DPDK</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-purple/20 text-tag-purple border border-tag-purple/40">F-Stack</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- 5-Stage RISC-V -->
          <article class="hover-lift group rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 sm:p-5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-tag-orange/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-8px_rgba(206,145,120,0.25)] transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-display font-bold text-tag-orange mb-2">
              <a href="https://github.com/angad-singh97/riscv-core-verilog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">
                5-Stage Pipelined RISC-V Core
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-tag-orange/90 mb-2 font-medium">RV64IM, 5-stage pipeline</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light mb-2 leading-snug">Data Forwarding Unit for RAW hazards without stalling. 2-bit dynamic branch predictor. 2-way set-associative cache (write-back, write-allocate).</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-orange/20 text-tag-orange border border-tag-orange/40">SystemVerilog</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-purple/20 text-tag-purple border border-tag-purple/40">Verilator</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- LuigiDB -->
          <article class="hover-lift group rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 sm:p-5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-terminal-green/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-8px_rgba(78,201,176,0.25)] transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-display font-bold text-terminal-green mb-2">
              <a href="https://github.com/angad-singh97/luigi-db" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">
                LuigiDB â€” Geo-Distributed Transactions
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-terminal-green/90 mb-2 font-medium">2-WRTT commit, 30â€“60Ã— vs OCC</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light mb-2 leading-snug">Timestamp-ordered execution. Built on Mako (OSDI'25). TPC-C on cloud with simulated network latency.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-cpp-blue/20 text-cpp-blue border border-cpp-blue/40">C++</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-terminal-green/20 text-terminal-green border border-terminal-green/40">Mako</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Raft -->
          <article class="hover-lift group rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 sm:p-5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-accent-cyan/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-8px_rgba(34,211,238,0.25)] transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-display font-bold text-accent-cyan mb-2">
              <a href="https://github.com/angad-singh97/dslabs-cpp-angad-singh97" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">
                Raft Consensus in C++
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-accent-cyan/90 mb-2 font-medium">Replicated state machine (6.824-style)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light mb-2 leading-snug">Leader election with randomized timeouts, log replication via AppendEntries, RPC handlers. Thread-safe state machine; all 8 correctness tests passing.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-cpp-blue/20 text-cpp-blue border border-cpp-blue/40">C++</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Paxos -->
          <article class="hover-lift group rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 sm:p-5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-tag-pink/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-8px_rgba(255,121,198,0.25)] transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-display font-bold text-tag-pink mb-2">
              <a href="https://github.com/angad-singh97/paxos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">
                Paxos-Based Distributed Transaction System
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-tag-pink/90 mb-2 font-medium">Fault-tolerant distributed bank, Multi-Paxos over gRPC</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light mb-2 leading-snug">Prepare/Promise with ballot codes; async consensus via CompletableFuture and gRPC; catch-up for lagging nodes. Java, Spring Boot, Protobuf.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-pink/20 text-tag-pink border border-tag-pink/40">Java</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg bg-tag-purple/20 text-tag-purple border border-tag-purple/40">gRPC</span>
            </div>
