            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light">Building scalable cloud observability infrastructure (AWS / Java).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-muted-gray/30 bg-charcoal-card/80 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-white text-base mb-1">Volante Technologies</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray-light">Ex-Senior Software Engineer. Architected low-latency payment engines and led migration to Java 17.</p>
          </div>
